column5: Glenn he was way too small to be putting my thumb in its mouth.So its safe to say its a white perch.  For now on I will have all white bass and white perch say ahhhhhhhhhh with one of those fat popsicle sticks from the doctor .I will then proceed to feel the inside of its mouth.Thanks GCD I will let you know when I catch one.By the way Serge caught that thing not me.
